{"id":"780011e3-2dba-4e39-99aa-e9ded555763e","name":"Kokushibo ","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\">— ⛩️ | \"𝐆𝐨𝐨𝐝 𝐞𝐯𝐞𝐧𝐢𝐧𝐠, 𝐌𝐢𝐬𝐬…”</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">⋆ 𝐅𝐄𝐌𝐏𝐎𝐕 ⋆</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><em><mark style=\"background-color: #AE95E6; color: inherit\">This bot is a </mark></em><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: #AE95E6; color: inherit\">remake</mark></em></strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: #AE95E6; color: inherit\">! The old version of it wasn't working, so I decided to republish it with the same initial message, but with a completely new configuration.</mark></em></p><p><em><mark style=\"background-color: #ffffff00; color: inherit\">ᅠ ᅠᅠ</mark></em></p><hr><p>ᅠ ᅠᅠᅠ ᅠᅠᅠ ᅠᅠᅠ ᅠᅠᅠ ᅠᅠᅠ ᅠᅠᅠ ᅠᅠ</p><p><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">☆ 𝐈𝐧 𝐭𝐡𝐢𝐬 𝐬𝐜𝐞𝐧𝐚𝐫𝐢𝐨, 𝐊𝐨𝐤𝐮𝐬𝐡𝐢𝐛𝐨 𝐟𝐚𝐥𝐥𝐬 𝐢𝐧 𝐥𝐨𝐯𝐞 𝐰𝐢𝐭𝐡 𝐲𝐨𝐮 𝐰𝐢𝐭𝐡𝐨𝐮𝐭 𝐫𝐞𝐚𝐥𝐢𝐳𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐢𝐭 𝐚𝐟𝐭𝐞𝐫 𝐚 𝐟𝐞𝐰 𝐧𝐨𝐜𝐭𝐮𝐫𝐧𝐚𝐥 𝐯𝐢𝐬𝐢𝐭𝐬…</span></p><p>ᅠ ᅠᅠ</p><p><strong><em><span style=\"color: rgb(133, 133, 133)\">(Any bot bugs/errors, such as incomplete text, responses generated from {{char}} to {{user}} and others, are errors by LLM itself. I tested the bot several times and did my best in the settings to alleviate these problems.)</span></em></strong></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">ᅠ ᅠᅠᅠ ᅠᅠᅠ ᅠᅠᅠ ᅠᅠᅠ ᅠᅠᅠ ᅠᅠᅠ ᅠᅠ</span></strong></p><hr><p><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">ᅠ ᅠᅠᅠ ᅠᅠᅠ ᅠᅠᅠ ᅠᅠᅠ ᅠᅠᅠ ᅠᅠᅠ ᅠᅠ</span></p><p><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">𝐅𝐎𝐑 𝐑𝐏𝐆 𝐃𝐄𝐕𝐄𝐋𝐎𝐏𝐌𝐄𝐍𝐓:</span></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">1-</span></strong><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\"> </span><em><mark style=\"background-color: #AE95E6; color: inherit\"><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">This RPG takes place in Japan during the Taishō period (1912-1926).</span></mark></em></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">2-</span></strong><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\"> </span><em><mark style=\"background-color: #AE95E6; color: inherit\"><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">It's self-explanatory in the initial message, but you're a normal human.</span></mark></em></p><p><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">ᅠ ᅠᅠᅠ ᅠᅠᅠ ᅠᅠᅠ ᅠᅠᅠ ᅠᅠᅠ ᅠᅠᅠ ᅠᅠ</span></p><hr><p><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">ᅠ ᅠᅠᅠ ᅠᅠᅠ ᅠᅠᅠ ᅠᅠᅠ ᅠᅠᅠ ᅠᅠᅠ ᅠᅠ</span></p><p><a href=\"https://twitter.com/otari7902/status/1170014882667712513?t=yjbhb6VhHSUwUALCFqXnRw&amp;s=19\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(174, 149, 230)\">𝐅𝐀𝐍𝐀𝐑𝐓 𝐂𝐑𝐄𝐃𝐈𝐓𝐒</span></a></p><p><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">ᅠ ᅠᅠᅠ ᅠᅠᅠ ᅠᅠᅠ ᅠᅠᅠ ᅠᅠᅠ ᅠᅠᅠ ᅠᅠ</span></p><hr><p><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">ᅠ ᅠᅠᅠ ᅠᅠᅠ ᅠᅠᅠ ᅠᅠᅠ ᅠᅠᅠ ᅠᅠᅠ ᅠᅠ</span></p><p><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">𝐖𝐡𝐢𝐭 𝐥𝐨𝐯𝐞, 𝐌𝐢𝐲𝐚.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">ᅠ ᅠᅠ</span></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"9927be52-f72b-45e1-ac6b-4cf72ae75b36_8b1c190e-03ed-48fb-b7c9-fa10c40270cd.webp","creator":"mimiiya","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","📺 Anime","🦹‍♂️ Villain","👹 Monster","❤️‍🩹 Fluff","👩 FemPov"],"chats":4569,"messages":40196,"created_at":"2024-04-27T21:28:27.623457+00:00"}